# pilot
 
 - NYC Mesh account, free(no property of any kind) wifi network with our own router internet paid for a year
 - raspberry pi with public terminal connected to big screen and/or projector, and sound
 - operator/steward recruited who is regular, local
 - as open as possible, 24 hour screen display and wifi access from outside
 - pi crust media network, build social network of local content creators and community members who want to share resources of any kind
 - trash magic feed, trash to media flow
 - replication to more spaces is designed in